        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Stopping America's Foreign Enemies Through Rail And Infrastructure National Security Act or the SAFE TRAINS Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits railroad freight cars from operating on the U.S. freight railroad interchange system if the cars are manufactured in or use sensitive technologies from a country of concern or an affiliated state-owned enterprise. Countries of concern include nonmarket economies, those that inadequately protect intellectual property rights, and violators of certain foreign trade practices and agreements.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
